{"tid":826330,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"濕疹治療分享","createTime":"2018-09-18T07:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T12:34:08.000Z","uid":111417,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dbfee7b810ecc763b61ee97d8f726551014574eb","tid":826330,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"我記憶中濕疹係由小學6年級咁上下時間開始有, 我發病個病徵通常係腳小腿部份開始, 初頭有一小處痕, 跟住擴大, 最後漫延到成隻腳同大腿, 以前都有去睇下政府診所, 但次次都係開類固醇, 對我無乜用, 仲越查越痕添。<br />\n後來連類固醇都費事查了, 印象中細個屋企人帶過我返大陸打針, 都係有用既, 即日止痕, 跟住幾日完全消失晒, 不過太耐既事, 問唔返果啲係咩針。<br />\n<br />\n好, 講完一堆廢話, 入正題先。<br />\n上年無意中, 阿媽唔知係邊度拎咗樽咁既野俾我<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/152401_394659692a460258b45a99f1424ea357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F152401_394659692a460258b45a99f1424ea357.jpg&h=4b71b73c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/152415_efaf98db2eac3a61946ca0282ae6ddd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F152415_efaf98db2eac3a61946ca0282ae6ddd4.jpg&h=3c88a735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/152423_792069df363c9e9a3737d98e38ffb46e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F152423_792069df363c9e9a3737d98e38ffb46e.jpg&h=7233fd99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁啱當時隻腳有小小濕疹發咗出黎, 我就不妨一試既心態試下, 當時查落去有啲涼涼地既感覺, 都有啲止痕既效果, 於是查咗一日, 第二日原本紅紅地既濕疹變晒色無紅, 亦都無痕, 好似呢張圖咁(我每一次濕疹發出黎之後好返(自然好, 即係痕完一大輪之後), 就會變到咁樣, 啲皮膚啞晒色, 仲有啲好似麟咁既甩皮現象)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/152912_efc7da8df082905ed77570509e96f33c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F152912_efc7da8df082905ed77570509e96f33c.jpg&h=791bf568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住唔痕, 我就擺埋咗一邊無理佢, 直到一年後既今個月, 隻腳又有啲濕疹發出黎, 於是又諗起呢支野, 又拎返出黎查, 效果同上年一樣, 幾有效, 今次查咗2-3日又好返, 紅既地方轉咗啞色, 唔痕了。所以忍唔住, 想打番篇文同大家分享下。"},{"pid":"7b417735dc3e3ffd1a07cc3fa39d43bd42311bee","tid":826330,"uid":69698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"支野係邊買？"},{"pid":"8f197c737f74e530e416e43b1d885a16b7930a8f","tid":826330,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b417735dc3e3ffd1a07cc3fa39d43bd42311bee","tid":826330,"uid":69698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"支野係邊買？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"我都唔知, 係我媽俾我既。"},{"pid":"53de7589488c2bad300dca3a68aed361ff0da9b3","tid":826330,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"提一提, 有G6PD患者不可用此藥!!"},{"pid":"c94eb72e22449e6375637e12c459e6a9c6b4fce1","tid":826330,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:08:55.000Z","msg":"可能含鉛<br />\n小心<br />\n<br />\n香港應該唔俾入口<br />\n冇列明中草藥成份"},{"pid":"6e814e8cce849daa4fbed41afe29ac9e07e46f4b","tid":826330,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c94eb72e22449e6375637e12c459e6a9c6b4fce1","tid":826330,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:08:55.000Z","msg":"可能含鉛<br />\n小心<br />\n<br />\n香港應該唔俾入口<br />\n冇列明中草藥成份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:16:12.000Z","msg":"頭先上網search過, 啲人話裕華國貨, 華潤堂, 藥房同萬寧等有售, 應該符合政府規管。"},{"pid":"7817edc5a4850d40978e05564e9f7f7ed9e0a3a4","tid":826330,"uid":55830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53de7589488c2bad300dca3a68aed361ff0da9b3","tid":826330,"uid":111417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"提一提, 有G6PD患者不可用此藥!!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"我有牛皮但有G6PD<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\